com.delphix.masking.api.plugin.utils

Class PluginMetadata

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.delphix.masking.api.plugin.utils.PluginMetadata

  • public final class PluginMetadata
extends java.lang.Object
    This class supports discovery of metadata embedded in plugin JAR files, as well as serving as the transport object fort that data.

    • Method Detail

      • readManifest

        public static PluginMetadata readManifest(java.nio.file.Path jarFile)
        Read relevant attributes from the plugin JAR's manifest. This method is also responsible for trimming values to the maximum allowed field lengths by the Delphix engine.
        Parameters:
        jarFile - The plugin JAR file
        Returns:
        An object containing the value of all relevant attributes

      • jarPathToPluginName

        public static java.lang.String jarPathToPluginName(java.nio.file.Path jarPath)
        Convert a JAR path to the default plugin name for that JAR. The result will always be a legal plugin name but may conflict with an existing plugin name.
        Parameters:
        jarPath - The JAR path
        Returns:
        The default plugin name based on JAR path
